          "datePublished": "2023-05-03",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I like to share very positive feedback about Vedanya International School. The faculty and staff here are passionate and committed to creating a nurturing and supportive environment for their students. The school's focus on individualized attention and small class sizes has enabled a child to receive personalized instruction and support that has helped them excel in all spheres. Moreover, the school's emphasis on extracurricular activities has provided children with opportunities to explore their interests and passions beyond the classroom. They too have state-of-the-art sports facility, including sports and a well-stocked library which has helped children to develop love for reading and outdoor games. It is really very impressive to see how the school inspires a sense of social responsibility in their students. The school encourages students to be empathetic and compassionate towards others.\nOverall, I would highly recommend Vedanya School to any parent looking for a school that prioritizes academic excellence, character development, and social responsibility. The school's commitment to creating a well-rounded education for their students is truly exceptional, and I am grateful for the positive impact it has had on my child's overall development. Thank you Vedanya!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        }
